description: Cliff Diving, Jet Ski, Swimming, Paragliding.
Life Jackets will be provided to every person.
It’s something that you should do at least once in your life.
An instructor will be provided with the jet ski.
The only thing people love in summers. Don’t worry if you can’t swim there will be instructors and life jackets to help you swim.
Additional charges will be applied for paragliding.
Registration fee includes transport, food, swimming, jet ski, cliff diving and life jacket. The team of Next Events will be there to help you in every step.
